{
  "text": "In some situations it is possible to separate diagnosis and treatment, because they are two largely independent procedures. In these cases our analysis provides novel theoretical support for separation, complementing existing explanations. For example, in their discussions of separation between doctors and pharmacies, [CITATION_1] ",
